defaultWritten Submission from Liberty VEP0021default&#xa0;defaultAbout Libertydefault&#xa0;
defaultLiberty (The National Council for Civil Liberties) is one of the UK’s leading civil liberties and human rights organisations. Liberty works to promote human rights and protect civil liberties through a combination of test case litigation, lobbying, campaigning and research.
default&#xa0;
defaultLiberty Policydefault&#xa0;
defaultLiberty provides policy responses to Government consultations on all issues which have implications for human rights and civil liberties. We also submit evidence to Select Committees, Inquiries and other policy fora, and undertake independent, funded research.
